Recently, more people are found to suffer from depression, resulting from excessive strain and steep demand. Meanwhile, more people attempt to look for felicity. From a different perspective, while a life forced by zero mistake maybe gets the opposite of what we want, levity, sometimes, adds more colours to our life. It goes without saying that a life forced by zero mistake is stressful, painful and provoking to most people. On the contrary, if we dare to make mistakes and alleviate burdens on ourselves, we will lead a more beautiful life.
